# testing inj_jet setup with similar mesh
###################################################################
reset
###################################################################
create Cylinder height 20 radius 5 
rotate Volume 1 angle 90  about X include_merged

create Cylinder height 5 radius 1 
rotate Volume 2 angle 90  about X include_merged

move Volume 1  y 20 include_merged
move Volume 2  y 2.5 include_merged

align volume 1  source surface 3  target surface 5   include_merged

imprint all
merge all

#mesh
surface 6 size auto factor 5
surface 6 scheme circle interval 5 fraction 0.6
mesh surface 6

volume 2  redistribute nodes off 
volume 2  scheme Sweep  source surface 6    target surface 5   sweep transform least squares 
volume 2  autosmooth target on  fixed imprints off  smart smooth off 
mesh volume 2 

surface 7 scheme hole rad_intervals 5 bias -1
mesh surface 7 

volume 1  redistribute nodes off 
volume 1  scheme Sweep  source surface 7 5    target surface 2   sweep transform least squares 
volume 1  autosmooth target on  fixed imprints off  smart smooth off 
mesh volume 1

block 1 add volume all
block 1 element type HEX20

#inlet
sideset 1 add surface 6 
sideset 1 name "inlet"

#outlet
sideset 2 add surface 2
sideset 2 name "outlet"

#walls
sideset 3 add surface 1 7 4
sideset 3 name "walls"